<wi type="G" value="1510,11,">SOY</wi>.» </t>
</fr>

<cl/>
Judas also, who betrayed him, was standing with them.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="1161,13,">Y</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2532,14,">también</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2455,15,">Judas</wi>,
