<wi type="G" value="2476,12,">estaba</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3326,19,">con</wi>
<wi type="G" value="846,20,">ellos</wi>. </t>
</sv>
<sv id="Juan-18-6">
When therefore he said to them, «I AM,»
they went backward, and fell to the ground.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="3767,2,">Entonces</wi>
<wi type="G" value="5613,1,">tan pronto</wi>
<wi type="G" value="846,4,">les</wi>
