<fr>«Who are you  looking for?»
<t xml:lang="es">«¿<wi type="G" value="5101,5,">A quién</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2212,6,">buscan</wi>?» </t>
</fr>
<cl/>
They said, «Jesus of Nazareth.»
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="3588,7,"/><wi type="G" value="1161,8,">Y</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2036,9,">ellos dijeron</wi>,
«<wi type="G" value="2424,10,">Jesús</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,11,"><wi type="G" value="3480,12,">de Nazaret</wi></wi>.» </t>

</sv></cm>

<cm>
<sv id="Juan-18-8">
Jesus answered,
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="3588,2,"><wi type="G" value="2424,3,">Jesús</wi></wi>
<wi type="G" value="611,1,">respondió</wi>, </t>
<fr>«I told you that I AM. If therefore you seek
